item.title: nginx talk on FLISOL at UIA
item.description: Friends, I’ll be attending the FLISOL (Latin American Free Software Install Fest) conference in Universidad Iberoamericana, this Friday, where I’ll be talking about how marvelous nginx is and why you should use it. If you are near, you should stop by! Tell of your co-workers and friends, it’ll be fun.
